      "author": "RobertttBS",
      "description": "### 🚀 Enhancements\r\n- **Multi-Window Support**: Click handlers + timers fixed in pop-out windows. Resolves canvas metadata clicks.\r\n- **Settings UI**: Switch headers to native `Setting().setHeading()`.\r\n- **Text Casing**: Menu renamed \"Split by Headings\" -> \"Split by headings\".\r\n\r\n### 🛠️ Code Quality\r\n- **Type Safety**: Replace `any` -> strict Canvas types.\r\n- **ESLint & API**: Fix signature mismatches (`onunload`, `onClose`), fix regex escapes, add lint directives.\r\n- **Memory/Lifecycle**: Scope markdown renderer to modal lifetime.",
